metadata.name: Hurricane
metadata.description:
Hurricane by Cryptopoetess x Nhefertiti

Caught between 
The ocean of thought 
And sea of words 
My lips buoyed in the center 
Who I want to be 
And who I present to be 
A hurricane of identity 
Forgetting that I myself 
Am water 
That can shift and change 
From a raging current 
To a cumulus on a summers day 
Or the tear on a lovers cheek
I am everything, everywhere 
I am what I choose to be 
So I choose to be me.

Digital art  
4096 x 2160 px
